<h1 id="project-4-flocking">Project 4: Flocking</h1>

<p>The goal of this project was to create a flock of 20 robots, which show good heading agreement based on the paper ‚ÄúReynolds flocking in reality with fixed-wing robots: communication range vs. maximum turning rate‚Äù. Robot start in random positions and orientations. The ‚Äúflocks‚Äù should be designed to look like the left scenario below</p>

